  <h1><u>7 WONDERS OF THE WORLD</u></h1>
  <p>
    <b>"THE 7 WONDERS OF THE WORLD"</b> are the wonderful sculptures. All of them are built by great people of our history. All of them have a unique speciality in them which make the people wonder about them. Now let us have a look at them.
  </p>
  <p><h3>The 7 wonders of the world are:</h3></p>
  <div>
  <ul><h3>
      <li><b>THE TAJ MAHAL</b></li>
      <li><b>THE GREAT WALL OF CHINA</b></li>
      <li><b>CHRIST THE REDEEMER STATUE</b></li>
      <li><b>COLOSSEUM</b></li>
      <li><b>MACHU PICCHU</b></li>
      <li><b>PETRA</b></li>
    <li><b>THE CHICHEN ITZA</b></li></h3>
    </ul>

  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/06/05/21/09/cultural-tourism-5264542__340.jpg">
  </div><br>
  <p><b><h1>"THE TAJ MAHAL"</h1></b></p>
  <p>The Taj Mahal is built by a mughal emperor named <b>SHAH JAHAN</b> between 1628-1658. It was built by him after the death of his wife <b>MUMTAZ</b> to show his love towards her and that's why it is called the "SYMBOL OF LOVE". </p>
  <div>
    
    <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/photos/the-great-wall-of-china-picture-id899508826?b=1&k=6&m=899508826&s=170667a&w=0&h=P-_ScyeGSN1fLCP5cIAk9zo9fH85xpUlS7AKjX5cWUg=">
  </div><br>
    <h1><b>"THE GREAT WALL OF CHINA"</b></h1>
    <p>The Great Wall Of China is the longest wall in the world. It is <b>21,196</b> km long. It was built by a chinese emperor named "<b>EMPEROR QIN SHI HUANG</b>" in 221 B.C. </p>
     <div>
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/01/15/21/49/rio-de-janeiro-1142442__340.jpg">
     </div>
    <h1><b>"CHRIST THE REEEMER STATUE"</b></h1>
    <p>Christ The Redeemer [statue] is a very wonderful statue of lord "<b>JESUS CHRIST</b>". In the statue his arms spread upto 28 metres. It was built by many statue artists and is 38 metre high.</p>
    <div>
      <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/photos/colosseum-in-rome-and-morning-sun-italy-picture-id539115110?b=1&k=6&m=539115110&s=170667a&w=0&h=m52kg-2ufEALCN848XXHflzzL_z75VauZksXUbOTcv4=">
    </div>
    <h1><b>"COLOSSEUM"</b></h1>
    <p>The Colosseum  is the largest ancient amphitheatre ever built. It was built by Emperor <b>VESPASIAN</b> between 69-79 AD.</p>
    <div>
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2012/04/26/22/48/machu-picchu-43387__340.jpg">
    </div>
    <h1><b>"MACHU PICCHU"</b></h1>
    <p>Machu Picchu was built in 15th century at the height of the <b>INCA EMPIRE</b> located in the Eastern Cordillera of southern Peru. It is an example of great architecture by the people who lived earlier. </p>
    <div><img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2020/03/29/21/44/petra-4982346__340.jpg"></div>
    <h1><b>PETRA</b></h1>
    <p>Petra is a historic and archaeological place located in southern Jordan. It exists from nearly <b>7000 B.C.</b>. It was built by <b>NABATEANS</b></p>
    <div>
      <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/photos/kukulkan-el-castillo-mayan-pyramid-chichen-itza-mexico-picture-id527550100?b=1&k=6&m=527550100&s=170667a&w=0&h=5Ro-2bINYxLdKmDCzrTT6928F1uQOgEOvoDYu4nt2O8=">
    </div>
    <h1><b>"THE CHICHEN ITZA"</b></h1>
    <p>The Chichen Itza was built by "<b>MAYA</b>" people between 900–1200 AD. It is located in Yucatán, Mexico.</p>
